{"tid":2080122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥身穿黑色素服出席李鵬飛追思會","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T09:05:17.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd1f7505c34593c30b3de5bf0bbb8e4d65f96b4","tid":2080122,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:15:01.000Z","msg":"前行政立法兩局議員、自由黨創黨主席李鵬飛上月離世，家人今日在灣仔會展為李鵬飛舉行追思會。多名政商界人士到場致意，其中身穿黑色素服的行政長官林鄭月娥下午三點半左右到場，逗留不足十分鐘後離開，到場前後都未有發言。多名曾與李鵬飛在議會共事的議員，包括民主黨劉慧卿、楊森；黨友周梁淑怡和劉健儀等先後到場致意。<br />\n<br />\n場地中央放有李鵬飛生前穿著西裝的遺照，兩旁的屏幕亦播放多張李鵬飛生前，主持自由黨創黨儀式，以及主持電視節目等的照片。靈堂中央放有特首及三名司長的花圈，當中林鄭月娥送上的花圈寫上「德望流徽」；長和系創辦人李嘉誠、中大校長段崇智，前特首曾蔭權等人亦有送上花圈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1320971&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1320971%26csid%3D261_341&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=d4be8d71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1320971&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ff7677896adb1630fce8b98e84276a309f84a12f","tid":2080122,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExR2F1o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExR2F1o.jpg&h=7330a582&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咩表情嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a32e29d532690e5735ef7f5eeb4e194b372984","tid":2080122,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0832ad74062b99f34c71eec419f25a56a1fdf8b2","tid":2080122,"uid":76680,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"竟然著黑色衫"},{"pid":"1f01e406b9f4d1a9bdb9820fea4263721869d76d","tid":2080122,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"